<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>جَعَلْتُهَا شِعْرَاً لِتَلْفِتَ الْفِطَنْ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَالشِّعْرُ لِلْحِكْمَةِ مُذْ كَانَ وَطَنْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَخَيْرُ مَا يُنْظَمُ لِلأَدِيبِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>مَا رَدَّدَتْهُ أَلْسُنُ التَّجْرِيبِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَلْقَى غُلاَمٌ شَرَكَاً يَصْطَادُ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَكُلُّ مَنْ فَوْقَ الأَرْضِ صَيَّادُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَانحَدَرَتْ عُصْفُورَةٌ مِنَ الشَّجَرْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>لَمْ يَنهَهَا النَّهْيُ وَلاَ الحَزْمُ زَجَرْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>قَالَتْ سَلاَمٌ أَيُّهَا الْغُلاَمُ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>قَالَ عَلَى الْعُصْفُورَةِ السَّلاَمُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>قَالَتْ صَبيٌّ مُنحَني الْقَنَاةِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قَالَ حَنَتْهَا كَثْرَةُ الصَّلاَةِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>قَالَتْ أَرَاكَ بَادِيَ الْعِظَامِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>قَالَ بَرَتْهَا كَثْرَةُ الصِّيَامِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>قَالَتْ فَمَا يَكُونُ هَذَا الصُّوفُ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>قَالَ لِبَاسُ الزَّاهِدِ المَوْصُوفُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>سَلِي إِذَا جَهِلْتِ عَارِفِيهِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فَابْنُ أَدْهَمَ وَالْفُضَيْلُ فِيهِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>قَالَتْ لِمَ الْعَصَا أَخَا الإِسْلاَمِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>قَالَ بِهَا أَمْشِي وَسْطَ الظَّلاَمِ<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>